Okay Avatar fans! The first  NEW episode will be aired on July 14th at 8pm/7pmC. That will happen everyday up until the 2 HOUR Finale on July 19th at 8pm/7pmC!

So don't miss it! ^_^

Hello there!

So ever since I saw that one episode of D-Gray Man at Colassal Con, I've become interested in it. So I started reading the manga and it's pretty good. The anime isn't out in America yet ( XP ) but it's coming out in 2009. I want to go buy the manga because it was released on May 6th, 2008!

Anyway, I've been in the mood for a new manga/anime ever since I finished reading Inuyasha. So... got any suggestions? I prefer romance, action/adventure, and fantasy but I'll try anything! ^_^ 

Got anything good?

For those who watch Avatar and don't know: The next two episodes of Avatar have been leaked!

Go to www.avatarchapter.com or YouTube and look up the name AFlyingBison. I like the ones on YouTube better because it has a better quality and takes less time to load.

Howeverm remember to continue to watch Avatar on Nick so they will have good ratings!! ^-^
